As far as spells, do not buy Flare. Flare is useless. The Mage Compendium is great for seeing what spells you get at what level, and seeing what they do. <br>
Also, I am sure it has been said before, but look at <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/" target="top">everquest.allakhazam.com/</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->. Under the section of quests by zone, look for those in Felwithe, and look for Art Keeper's armor. The link is <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/qsearch.html?zone=55" target="top">Here</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->. Do these as soon as possible, as they can net some nice armor. Honestly, I would label your priorities as<br>
1)Bags<br>
2)Spells<br>
3)Quests<br>
