<br>
I would add one suggestion, which might be easily overlooked because of who we are and why we chose this class:<br>
<br>
Start grouping. <br>
<br>
Find some friends and start hunting with them. You'll be able to take on more formidable opponents, you'll make a little money, and you'll learn the strengths and limitations of other classes.<br>
<br>
I've known Magicians who were running around at level 50, wearing mostly level 30-ish gear, simply because they soloed virtually all the time, and were limited because of it - don't fall into the trap! Start making connections now, and it will reward you down the road. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
